org.aksw.simba.hibiscus

Class HibiscusSourceSelection

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.aksw.simba.hibiscus.HibiscusSourceSelection

  • public class HibiscusSourceSelection
extends java.lang.Object
    Perform triple pattern-wise source selection using FedSumaries, cache or SPARQL ASK. Note that this is first phase of our source selection. In second phase we perform source filtering for each of the statement pattern using Hyper Graphs
    Author:
    Saleem

    • Method Detail

      • performSourceSelection

        public java.util.Map<org.openrdf.query.algebra.StatementPattern,java.util.List<com.fluidops.fedx.algebra.StatementSource>> performSourceSelection(java.util.HashMap<java.lang.Integer,java.util.List<org.openrdf.query.algebra.StatementPattern>> DNFgrps)
                                                                                                                                           throws org.openrdf.repository.RepositoryException,
                                                                                                                                                  org.openrdf.query.MalformedQueryException,
                                                                                                                                                  org.openrdf.query.QueryEvaluationException
        Perform triple pattern-wise source selection for the provided statement patterns of a SPARQL query using HiBISCuS Summaries, cache or remote ASK queries. Remote ASK queries are evaluated in parallel using the concurrency infrastructure of FedX. Note, that this method is blocking until every source is resolved. Recent SPARQL ASK operations are cached for future use. The statement patterns are replaced by appropriate annotations in this process. Hypergraphs are created in step 1 of source selection and are used in step 2 i.e. prunning of triple pattern-wise selected sources.
        Parameters:
        DNFgrps - Set of BGP's in SPARQL Query
        Returns:
        stmtToSources Map of triple patterns to relevant sources
        Throws:
        org.openrdf.query.QueryEvaluationException - Query Exe Error
        org.openrdf.query.MalformedQueryException - Query Error
        org.openrdf.repository.RepositoryException - Repository Error
